content:
You are here:

Merge Duplicate Cases from the Case Record Home

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To view cases:	Read on cases
To create cases:	Create on cases
To edit cases:	Edit on cases
To delete cases:	Delete on cases

Open the case that you want to merge.
Click the arrow to open the menu in the highlights panel.
Click Merge Cases
Use the search bar to browse for cases that you want to merge.
Select up to three cases.
Click Next.
Select the master record and field values.
Click Next.
Click Merge.
The merged case is created, with non-master cases deleted if setup allows.
title: Merging Duplicate Cases in Service Cloud
